@node Main "Columnar - Documentation"

                           'Columnar' 1.0

                        by Charles-N. Jacob

  'Columnar' is a @{" Workbench game " link play} where there are 8 columns, 2 of
which are high enough to reach and support a 'roof'. The idea is to
remove part of columns so that the roof goes down, at least to the
level of 2 platforms that are located on either sides of the game
board.

  What complicates matters a little, is that when a column is being
lowered, another will randomly rise, up to the roof height.

  Complete the game in the least amount of moves...

  Have fun!

