@node play "The game: Installation/Playing"

                             Installation

  The installation is very simple, just place 'Columnar' where you
want on your hard drive, floppy disk, Ram Disk, etc. No other files
or Libraries are needed.

                             How to play?

  Gameplay is simple: click on any part of a column, to make it go
down, another column will randomly increase in height... until it
reaches the roof. You can also click on an empty space betwwen the
roof and the top of a column, this will make it go up, and another
column will decrease in height.

  As columns are lowered, when all of them are separated from the
roof, then the roof will drop to a lower level... The game is
completed when the roof is at the same level as the platforms that
are located on either sides of the game board.

  That's all there is to it... Now go play the game! :)

  Have fun!

  To quit the game, click on the game window's close button or
press the 'Esc' key.

@endnode

